---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Container from '@/components/tailus/Container.astro'
import Frame from '@/components/tailus/Frame.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Meet the Founder - Pixelated Empathy"
  description="The inspiring journey of a mental health professional who became an AI developer to solve real-world healthcare training challenges"
  bgType="dark"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 lg:py-32">
    <Container>
      <div class="lg:w-2/3 text-center mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-500 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-8">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          From Therapist to Tech Founder
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          When Mental Health Expertise
          <span class="text-purple-500">Meets AI Innovation</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          One person's journey from addiction counselor to AI developer, building the future of mental health training through technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Journey -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <Container>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            The Problem That Changed Everything
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              After years working as an addiction counselor and attachment specialist, I witnessed firsthand how inadequate training left many therapists unprepared for complex cases. Traditional training methods were inconsistent, expensive, and failed to provide the real-time feedback needed for skill development.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              I saw therapists struggling with unconscious bias, missing critical emotional cues, and lacking confidence in their clinical decisions. The result? Patients weren't getting the quality care they deserved, and therapists were burning out from the pressure.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
              The breaking point came when I realized that the same patterns repeated across institutions nationwide. This wasn't just a local problem—it was a systemic failure affecting thousands of mental health professionals and their patients.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">The Statistics That Drove Me</h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>70% of therapists report feeling undertrained for complex cases</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-orange-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Training costs average $15,000 per therapist annually</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Traditional training lacks real-time feedback mechanisms</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Quality varies dramatically between training programs</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Pivot -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          The Leap from Counseling to Code
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          How domain expertise led to technical innovation
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.672 1.911a1 1 0 10-1.932.518l-.259.966a1 1 0 001.932.518l.26-.966zM8.66 5.782a1 1 0 10-1.932.517l-.259.966a1 1 0 001.932.518l.26-.966zM11.32 5.782a1 1 0 10-1.932.517l-.259.966a1 1 0 001.932.518l.26-.966zM13.98 1.911a1 1 0 10-1.932.518l-.259.966a1 1 0 001.932.518l.26-.966z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            The Self-Taught Journey
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Starting with Python for data analysis, I spent 18 months learning full-stack development, AI/ML, and cloud architecture. Every line of code was written with a therapist's understanding of what clinicians actually need.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            The Technical Breakthrough
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Understanding both therapy workflows and AI capabilities allowed me to create something unique: a platform that trains therapists the way they actually think and work, not just how technologists think they should.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.49 3.17c-.38-1.56-2.6-1.56-2.98 0a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.286.948c-1.372-.836-2.942.734-2.106 2.106.54.886.061 2.042-.947 2.287-1.561.379-1.561 2.6 0 2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01.947 2.287c-.836 1.372.734 2.942 2.106 2.106a1.532 1.532 0 012.287.947c.379 1.561 2.6 1.561 2.978 0a1.532 1.532 0 012.287-.947c1.372.836 2.942-.734 2.106-2.106a1.532 1.532 0 01.947-2.287c1.561-.379 1.561-2.6 0-2.978a1.532 1.532 0 01-.947-2.287c.836-1.372-.734-2.942-2.106-2.106a1.532 1.532 0 01-2.287-.947zM10 13a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            The Innovation Advantage
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            My clinical background gave me insights no pure technologist could have: understanding therapeutic relationships, recognizing subtle emotional patterns, and knowing what actually helps therapists grow professionally.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Technical Achievement -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Built for Scale, Designed for Impact
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Enterprise-grade technology built from real-world experience
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Enterprise Architecture from Day One
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">HIPAA & FHE Dual Compliance</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Built privacy-first with healthcare industry standards from the ground up, not as an afterthought.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Real-Time AI Processing</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Bias detection and emotion analysis that provides immediate feedback during training sessions.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Global Edge Network</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Sub-100ms response times worldwide with 300+ edge locations for enterprise scalability.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Quantified Outcomes</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Measurable improvements: 40% faster training, 85% better effectiveness, 60% cost reduction.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Technical Milestones
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">First AI Model</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Built initial bias detection algorithm</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">HIPAA Compliance</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Achieved healthcare industry security standards</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Enterprise Ready</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Scaled to support 500+ healthcare institutions</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-emerald-500 font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Global Deployment</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">99.9% uptime across 300+ edge locations</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Vision -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          The Future We're Building
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Scaling mental health expertise globally through AI innovation
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 p-1 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <blockquote class="text-center">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 italic mb-6">
              "I believe that every therapist deserves world-class training, regardless of their location or institution's budget. By combining my clinical experience with AI technology, we're making expert-level mental health training accessible to everyone who needs it."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              — Founder, Pixelated Empathy
            </cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-500 mb-1">500+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Healthcare Institutions</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-500 mb-1">15,000+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Trained Therapists</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">85%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Effectiveness Improvement</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <!-- The Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600">
    <Container>
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Ready to Transform Mental Health Training?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join the movement to make expert-level mental health training accessible to every healthcare professional worldwide.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/demo" class="bg-white text-purple-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors">
            Experience the Platform
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">
            Partner With Us
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-purple-100 text-sm mt-4">
          Built by a therapist, for therapists • HIPAA compliant • Enterprise ready
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>